text: The Alfa Romeo 125 is an Italian piston aircraft engine made by Alfa Romeo in the 1930s. between 1934 and 1944 there where 11,000 units built. == Variants == * Alfa 125 R.C.10 * Alfa 125 R.C.35 == Users == * Breda Ba.64 * Savoia- Marchetti S.M.81 Pipistrello Category:Alfa Romeo aircraft engines
